  "text": "The operational matrix of fractional derivatives has been determined for some types of orthogonal polynomials, such as Chebyshev polynomials [CITATION_1] and Legendre polynomials [CITATION_2] , and for integration has been determined for several types of orthogonal polynomials, such as Chebyshev polynomials [CITATION_3] , Laguerre series [CITATION_4] , and Legendre polynomials [CITATION_5] . Recently, the Bernstein operational matrix approach is developed for solving a system of high order linear Volterra-Fredholm integro-differential equations in [CITATION_6] .",
